# Changelog

## v1.0.0

Initial JMX release.

- Renamed and reorganized the client as JMX.
- Reworked the main experience with an Apple-inspired Liquid Glass design direction.
- Added home discovery, search, recommendations, comic detail, comments, favorites, history, reading, and download flows.
- Added JM account login, profile, check-in, and synchronized account data.
- Added local cache trimming and APK size optimizations.
- Embedded the required AndroidLiquidGlass Backdrop module under `third_party/AndroidLiquidGlass/backdrop` for reproducible builds.
- Added disclaimer and open-source credits pages.
